{"tid":1661483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【五區快閃●中環】銀行OL取消歐遊堅持遊行 哭訴：我地係唔會驚！","createTime":"2019-10-18T06:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T19:28:25.000Z","uid":8968,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"62411987da7946aa8caaa2f475481243890f72d4","tid":1661483,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191018/large/1571379372_c51d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191018%2Flarge%2F1571379372_c51d.jpg&h=b4949760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中環白領儷人Tyson今午12時許一個人於遮打花園等待快閃行動開始，她腳踏一雙高跟鞋，穿著絲質上衣及短褲，滿頭大汗地站在遮打花園一角。她指自己從事銀行業，今年2月才從美國返港當實習生，Tyson自稱是和理非，表示由六月起多次參與反送中運動，「其實我行出去都好驚呀！真係驚到手都震晒呀！但我哋做嘅嘢只係好少咋！如果我哋嚟到呢個時候話驚，要縮，你對唔對得住喺前面流血嘅人？你對唔對得住喺前線俾人拉咗嘅人？」<br />\n<br />\nTyson受訪時表現相當激動，她聲淚俱下的說：「你哋咁樣係唔會令我驚！我唔會移民避開混亂！我點解要走！呢度係我屋企呀！」她坦言六月至今，被林鄭月娥點燃起心中所有怒火，「我原本暑假安排晒去歐洲旅行，但呢場運動發生，我全部取消晒！」<br />\n她直言自己雖然出席所有和理非行動，但其實付出的遠遠不及其他勇敢的用伴，「我點做都唔夠啲前線示威者犧牲得多」。Tyson稱自己每次談到近月社會事件，心情都相當激憤，但她指上百萬香港人在近月的付出令她很感動，「總之一句講晒，五大訴求，缺一不可，不割席，不分化！團結係最緊要呀！」<br />\n<br />\n女手足好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bf8191d565606a960a150bf0c6d0c9aeed4567","tid":1661483,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"Twitter係每日必做的任務<br />\n禁兩個制都懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲同我retweet哂去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日國際新聞關香港或者抵制中國事的有：<br />\nDior (向中國道歉，承認台灣係中國）<br />\n<br />\nBlizzard(共雪禁左美國大學隊賽半年，原因係美國大學隊支持Free Hong Kong)<br />\n<br />\nDreamwork（動畫畫九段線，畫出大部分的南海係屬於中國，菲律賓嚴重抗議，荷蘭海牙仲裁已經響2016裁定九段線違反聯合國國際公約，所以Dreamwork 奶共奶到洗緊細路腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nnba (Lebron James 鬧Morey咩都唔知就亂tweet，大家可以提出任何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=78f2b336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以搵到以上的新聞<br />\n<br />\nRetweet 加 cm ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得每日做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你入 /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就可以見到人權法新聞同議員的tweet<br />\n<br />\n記得多謝埋人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac318c4bc937d981e831e60fbd65ff4715c494ae","tid":1661483,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家幫我推多次上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n等我為大家回憶下決定1020去定唔去[2]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657270</a>"},{"pid":"402d16ea874ab00b80cf1270417a29d1a324ed4a","tid":1661483,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"好似幾正"},{"pid":"dbad4102f3df20aaaa27c61a85c774abf5737325","tid":1661483,"uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"402d16ea874ab00b80cf1270417a29d1a324ed4a","tid":1661483,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"好似幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可惜蘋果攝記唔影全身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/f